# Files gitignored but needed inside every Agent-View worktree.
# Syntax is .gitignore-style. Only files that match a pattern AND are
# gitignored are copied; tracked files are never duplicated.
#
# See docs/PARALLEL-WORK.md for the rationale per entry.

# Session orientation: STATE.md, HARDWARE-TASKS-*.md, SESSIONS.md, BACKLOG.
# CLAUDE.md tells every session to read docs/_private/STATE.md first, so a
# worktree without this directory starts blind.
docs/_private/

# Future-proofing — no .env is checked in today, but if one ever lands here
# (locally), background sessions should inherit it.
.env
.env.local
